snippet.title: Milord Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Milord on Steam: store.steampowered.com/app/2455460/Milord/

Milord is a Kingdom Management RPG game. You'll be left with hard choices for your fiefdom. Will you be able to rise to the occasion or lose your kingdom and life in the process?

Developed by iBright Games
